title: Anna Obsessed (1977/VHSRip)
description: Sarring: Annette Haven, Constance Money, Suzanne McBain Hauntingly Seductive. She Could Only Be… This incredibly provocative film finds Anna (Constance Money) the victim of an attack. Following the incident, she becomes rather “hyper-sexual” and turns her attentions to other women for her sexual pleasure. Her jealous husband finds himself torn and yet needing an outlet and begins an almost comical affair at his office.
